Download link : ( https://www.mongodb.com/try/download/shell )

cd ~
touch .bash_profile 
ls -a  
vim .bash_profile
i (for insert)
alias mongod="/c/Program\ files/MongoDB/Server/4.0/bin/mongod.exe"
alias mongo="/c/Program\ Files/MongoDB/Server/4.0/bin/mongo.exe"
esc (escape)
:wq

Open the terminal again and write

mongo --version / mongos --version 
if worked properly then  it not shows that " bash not found ".


